@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant AuthService
participant IdentityProvider
participant AuditLog

User -> Frontend: Open Login Page
Frontend -> AuthService: POST /auth/login {username,password}
AuthService -> IdentityProvider: Validate credentials (Cognito)
IdentityProvider --> AuthService: JWT + refresh token
AuthService -> AuditLog: Log successful login
AuthService --> Frontend: Return JWT (set cookie) + user profile
Frontend -> Frontend: Establish SignalR connection (Authorization header)
Frontend --> User: Redirect to Dashboard
@enduml